item.description:
[BORRADOR]
1.- Descarga oh-my-zsh: - sudo sh -c &ldquo;$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)&quot;
2.- Agregar theme: - En .oh-my-zsh/themes/amuse_2021.zsh-theme
3.- Seleccionar el theme: - Con nano .zshrc agregamos el themea &ldquo;amuse-2021&rdquo;
Cambiar de shell: -$ chsh -s /bin/zsh
